					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Vblank time length isn't really an issue here.  You can comfortably transfer 192 bytes in a vblank, and that's enough to transfer a palette 6 times over.<br /><br />edit: PLA/STA loop is equally fast as a LDA xxxx,X \ STA loop, just smaller code.</div>

					
