					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">The ridiculously optimized 30 fps version of the &quot;Bad Apple&quot; video uses a self-modifying sequence of LDA #$xx/STA $2007 to copy 240 bytes while still having time to read back from CHR ROM where a third of the video data is stored.</div>

